com.ibm.cs.model

Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.cs.model.Product
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class representing a single product, can have zero or more batches registered under it. For example: Under 'toothpaste' category, you can have 'Colgate White 50ml', 'Colgate Red 50ml', 'Close Up White 10ml' products.
    Author:
    Dan Alejandro A. Vargas
    See Also:
    Category, Batch, Serialized Form
